divs: sighting detailsjust on my way home from work at 1-15 am,got out of my car to open gates of my house,just happened to look up and saw what looked like a blue ball of flame just above the trees but as it past over me it seemed to be a solid object ,watched it for about 5\6 seconds but it was travelling so fast it was out of range,it was also compleatly silent,it was travelling from east to west.
